Persona 2

Jane Doe

Dog owner with specific food preferences that wants to find coffee shops easier, and let others with similar preferences know where they can locate these shops.

As a new user, I want to be able to contribute by providing info to others users about vegan and dog friendly coffee shops.

tech: iPhone user, laptop user
needs: An app that can quickly find vegan shops that are pet friendly.
proficiency: Often uses her phone and laptop to work from home.
likes: Applications that include many ways to filter different things she's looking for.
dislikes: When applications are not inclusive and she cannot find what she's looking for, She has to do a bunch of resource to find one thing, not being able to access something on her phone.

registered user
Interaction flow:
Jane Doe signs into the coffee website
Website logs her in and takes Jane to the webpage
webpage displays box asking her to input filters to look for a shop, ask her to rate the last shop she chose, or see where other users have recently gone.
She clicks on the button asking her to rate the last coffee shop she visited
Website takes her to review page
Jane selects "dog friendly" "cozy" "quiet" as tags for coffeeshop
Jane clicks complete
Webpage saves her results
Jane clicks "sign out"
